            <title>[LU-14072] client evicitions with DIO</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14072</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is very easily reproduced by Lustre:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;dd if=/dev/zero of=data bs=1234 count=1&lt;br/&gt;
touch data1&lt;br/&gt;
dd if=/dev/data of=data1 bs=1M oflag=direct&lt;/p&gt;

